Package org.youscope.serverinterfaces

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ComponentProvider
    Interface to create measurement components like jobs or resources.
    ConstructionContext
    Interface handed over to addons during the construction/initialization of a measurement and its components.
    MeasurementProvider
    A class being able to construct new measurements.
    YouScopeLogin  
    YouScopeServer
    The main interface of the YouScope server, which controls the microscope, executes measurements, and similar.
    YouScopeServerProperties
    Interface providing information of the configuration and installed addons of the YouScope server.
